Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saturday Night
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,160cm
Comment: 0,0:22:25.12,0:22:34.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Self-Practice

Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.73,0:01:05.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.23,0:01:10.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Saturdays because Sawako cooks for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:12.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:20.56,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, my after-school ramen initiation never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:21.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:24.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so ready to have ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:28.06,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida-san was really upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:31.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't approve of light ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:33.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To hell with healthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:37.97,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But I had fun listening to Yoshida-san's ramen lecture over tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:41.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san, Yoshida-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.55,0:01:44.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curry tonight, huh, Sawako?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:49.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curry tonight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:50.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The phone's ringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:54.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Kuronuma residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.41,0:01:55.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignoring me tonight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:01.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako, it's from your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.05,0:02:07.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sadako,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:09.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're having ramen tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.55,0:02:11.07,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,We are?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:13.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, ramen revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:23.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go eat ramen with my friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:24.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:27.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sure, go, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:30.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't served the curry yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.32,0:02:32.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.43,0:02:34.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring them over sometime, Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:35.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:39.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:43.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did say that she's pretty happy these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:47.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, she came home a little later than usual the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:49.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is her friend a boy or a girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:51.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:03.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:08.00,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's my big ramen initiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:13.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, we don't have your cell number yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:14.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:16.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:17.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:22.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I needed one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:24.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:27.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let me know if you do get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:30.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:34.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chizu-chan, here with your friends tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:36.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Pops, can you cut us a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:39.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you win again, Chizu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:41.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:43.19,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted you to have the ramen here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:44.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:45.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have the usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:46.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:47.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your order?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:49.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I recommend miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:51.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have miso then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have shoyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:55.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just said I recommend miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:56.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:01.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not enough water.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:03.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:06.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you let your customers notice before you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:09.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's busy. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:09.71,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I just saw Sanada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:11.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, this is Ryu's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:16.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miso's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:22.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:24.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:28.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stuffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:30.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ramen's the best, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:34.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was twice as good since I was with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:36.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be heading upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:38.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, make yourselves at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:39.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:41.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:43.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was this your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:44.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:48.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:51.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:58.59,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida-san and Sanada-kun are really close, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:01.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, make yourself comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:04.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:07.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.31,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:16.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right now? Sorry, I'm with friends tonight. I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:19.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:20.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:23.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miso ramen's the best ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:23.21,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Houichi's ear was—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:24.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:27.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:28.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll text you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:29.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:31.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:32.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:34.56,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your current boyfriend's in University, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:38.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say “current.”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:41.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're so grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:43.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:47.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll know what it means to be a grown-up soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:50.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Chizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:56.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grown-up? You can't beat up 99 guys, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:06:00.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's such a half-assed record, 99 in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:02.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not half-assed, it's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:05.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have gone for 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:07.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the 100th like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:10.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:15.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on your combo breaker, Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:19.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a perfect time for you to come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:20.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:24.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:28.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two lovers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:38.68,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:40.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:45.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could at least confirm or deny, Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:45.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No don't confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:51.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're like brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:54.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, which is the older and younger brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:55.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:58.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your birthday's later than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:56.64,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, he called you a “brother.”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:58.23,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:07:01.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I had siblings as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:08.10,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:13.30,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Liveliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:17.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:26.84,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm allowed to be together with them, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:33.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we should invite Kazehaya too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:35.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:38.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let Ryu have a harem to himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:39.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:41.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harem...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:44.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel weird being the only guy here, Ryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:45.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pass me your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:47.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako, you call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:51.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:53.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:56.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me? I-Is it okay for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:57.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:07:58.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just call him already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:03.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to flip out when he finds out that a girl's calling from Ryu's phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:06.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit that button to call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:10.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm getting nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:14.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being so tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:16.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He picks it up himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.01,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Himself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.34,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me even more nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:24.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him to come now 'cause we're having a blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:27.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him Ryu's getting lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:33.67,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.56,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want him to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:50.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:52.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it, Shouta?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:52.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:54.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:56.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me talk to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:57.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk to Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:57.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:00.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Ryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:04.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Kazehaya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:06.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:11.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuro—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:12.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu's pho—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:15.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:18.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at Sanada-kun's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:20.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:23.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had ramen with Yano-san and Yoshida-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:26.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:32.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're having lots of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:37.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll be even more fun if you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.38,0:09:40.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bike down there really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:45.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:49.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew you were having so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:09.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:15.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You three were in the same class in middle school too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:16.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For grades eight and nine, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:19.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Ryu and Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:23.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He hasn't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:27.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been like this for as long as I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:29.85,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still growing though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:37.74,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kazehaya-kun in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:41.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is “The People's Kazehaya.”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:43.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's sort of younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:43.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:45.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he was in the baseball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.94,0:10:48.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is after his hair started growing back a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:51.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Ryu's bald, baseball club or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:52.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:55.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Ryu for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:10:59.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouta's good at baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:03.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pin was pissed that he didn't join the baseball team in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:07.20,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Kazehaya-kun I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:11.14,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of student he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:17.52,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he studied hard and practiced a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:21.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:22.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:25.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sports day is coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:27.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Kazehaya's going to be on the softball team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:29.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:34.63,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to see Kazehaya-kun as he'll be from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:40.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to be in photos with everyone, and much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:45.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of things are coming up—sports day, school trips...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:48.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:52.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:54.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll eat so much good food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.25,0:12:00.11,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get to talk about how much fun we're having with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:03.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:06.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Kurumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.23,0:12:09.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She picked up my papers once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:13.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:14.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:17.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she's popular with the guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:21.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of her, Ryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:24.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a type?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:29.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about her then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.43,0:12:35.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:39.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:44.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:49.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You freaked me out for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:54.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Kazehaya then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:05.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:08.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:10.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it's the same “love” as for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:12.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:14.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think she knows herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:16.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako, hey—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:21.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on, let her be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:26.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One has to climb the ladder to adulthood themselves, one step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:30.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it sound so wrong when you say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:39.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops, miso ramen, extra large!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:41.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming right up, Pin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:44.19,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:49.64,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That was about to get complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:50.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:56.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't, like, Kazehaya's hair longer than everyone else in the baseball club?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:59.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's hair grows really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:07.20,KimiTodo-Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,Korean/Japanese wisdom: A pervert's hair grows faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:01.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably a pervert, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.22,0:14:03.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Total closet pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:07.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a pervert, nor a closet pervert either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:08.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:11.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a total open pervert comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:16.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm normal, dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:17.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:19.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so half-assed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:22.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have said you're a mega pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:25.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:32.35,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a boy after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:35.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako's laughing, Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:38.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No laughing, Kuronuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:42.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't making fun of your—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:44.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:47.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:55.62,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart's racing more than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:59.58,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because I'm closer to him than when we're in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:05.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako, I mean Sawako,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:09.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come sit here, next to Chizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:13.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:14.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:19.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:28.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so soft, Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:30.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're, like, a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:32.24,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:33.54,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Our prince is in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:37.33,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, this is too fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:49.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playtime's over, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:51.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost, you angel of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:55.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go home, take a dump, and go to bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:58.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why is Arai-sensei here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:01.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were we too loud? Did we get reported?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:03.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.41,0:16:08.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the little league that this kid's dad runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:10.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've known him since he was a little brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:14.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you have no manners since you're a regular at Ryu's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:16.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:18.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, you wouldn't know, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:20.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:24.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw little old men run around after I looked into her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:31.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a little old man at my place too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:33.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:36.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pin, have you ever had sleep paralysis?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:39.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the time when I was a kid, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.88,0:16:41.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty often these days too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:45.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hear things in your room when it happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:49.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, my place is old. It creaks and cracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:52.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you've just got a psychic aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:58.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I couldn't sleep last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:17:01.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt something heavy on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:03.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:08.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might help if you bathe in salt water before you go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:10.16,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Purging salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:13.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes you feel warm and helps you sleep better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.98,0:17:19.26,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She knows how to banish spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:21.95,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I'm helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:22.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:26.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Pin, go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:28.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why don't you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:29.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:31.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:32.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:32.64,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, {\i1}now{\i0} you act like a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:34.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! It's closing time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:35.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we split?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:40.88,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a face like this as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:44.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:49.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:53.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have lots of fun from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:03.36,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Saturday night with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:05.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:09.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't believe I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:13.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading to the corner store, so I'm going that way too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:17.76,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart's racing, but I feel at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:19.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:21.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have at it, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:23.45,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:26.33,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:27.96,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:40.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to have lots of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:45.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Chizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:46.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Yano-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:53.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why are you going this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:54.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:56.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying, move over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:57.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:58.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be afraid going alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:03.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll go home and take a bath or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:04.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:07.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what kind of girl do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.78,0:19:08.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Type?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:12.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said Kurumi's not your type, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.16,0:19:16.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone blunt and simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:19.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some pretty obscure taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:20.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:22.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blunt and simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:24.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:27.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.44,0:19:30.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.07,0:19:32.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knew what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:39.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to tell me that you made up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:50.26,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart's still racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:53.60,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:20:00.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I'm in this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:03.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:08.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:10.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:14.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My life wouldn't have been the same without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:20.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make such a big deal out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:25.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I just wanted to try pouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:26.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pouting?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:29.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:33.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth is, I really just wanted peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:39.46,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,His face as it was in middle school,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:42.22,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,his face as it was for the first time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:47.44,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I got to see a different side of Kazehaya today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:50.96,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sort of happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:55.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you buying at the store, Kazehaya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:04.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:05.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:10.52,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And many more new faces from now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.01,0:22:27.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sunset sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.79,0:22:31.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a change in the wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.09,0:22:34.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Self-Practice
